---


Let's also add a navigation bar and footer to the layout. In the same file, under `<body>` add


= preserve do 
  - code("erb") do
    %nav.navbar.navbar-default.navbar-fixed-top
      .container
        %a.navbar-brand{href: "/"} The Idea app
        %ul.nav.navbar-nav
          %li.active
            %a{href: "/ideas"} Ideas

and before `</body>` add

= preserve do 
  - code("erb") do
    %footer
      .container
        Rails Girls 2014

Pay attention to the difference between `<body>` and `</body>`!